children.name: Rules
children.text:
This tiny series of rings on a chain resembles a miniature orrery depicting the stars in the sky. Each day after a long rest the wearer of this amulet gains access to 3 stars, which appear as motes of light that circle their head. One star can be used once as a reaction, granting one of the following benefits: 
- +2 to AC (this can cause an attack to miss)
- Teleport 15 feet to a spot the wearer can see (after a triggering attack is made)
- Allow an ally within 10 feet to reroll a saving throw
- Gain resistance to Radiant damage
